regionGB_up.title: Aero Sudah Terbaru
regionGB_up.description:
WhatsApp Base:  2.25.11.79

📜 Enable the menu option for managing people and groups.  
📜 Enable a more compact sticker keyboard design that displays 5 stickers in a row (previously it was 4). 
📜 Enable theme and bubble color settings in chats.  
📜 Enable the call link feature within chats and groups. 
📜 Enable blocking incoming messages from unknown accounts.
🔗 More fixes and other improvements.
